data.description: No homeowner association or HOA fees! Spacious 3 bedrooms/2 full bathroom home with a full unfinished basement and 2 car garage in Marietta. The home offers modern updates including all bathrooms, kitchen, and newer laminate flooring. The kitchen includes all appliances which includes the dishwasher, stove, and refrigerator. There is an exterior two-story unfinished detached garage great for storage, a workshop, or create a cute Airbnb for rental income - there is no plumbing but yes there is electricity in the two-story garage. This home is located close to schools, grocery stores, and restaurants.
